## ğŸ§ª Testing & Development

### Run Tests
```bash
# Run all tests
pytest

# Run specific test categories
pytest tests/test_strategies.py
pytest tests/test_risk_management.py
pytest tests/test_multi_market.py

# Run with coverage
pytest --cov=genebot
```

### Development Setup
```bash
# Install development dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run code formatting
black genebot/
flake8 genebot/

# Type checking
mypy genebot/
```

